{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:45:50.770Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Analyzing Imports**\n\nI'm currently focused on analyzing imports, specifically in `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. It looks like we're bringing in `DataTable`, `previewSupportTickets`, `TableColumn`, and `SupportTicket`. These imports are important context for understanding the scope of our work. It gives me a good lay of the land to start!\n\n\n**Confirming Imports Optimization**\n\nI've confirmed that importing `WorkspaceCard`, `MetricTile`, and `StatusBadge` is indeed possible from `@/components/private-app` as planned. The index file contains `export * from \"./cards-metrics-badges\";`, which is a relief! Now, I'm focusing on the code structure for `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`, and planning to define `EnrichedSupportTicket` and set up the state.\n\n\n**Defining State Parameters**\n\nI'm now defining the state parameters for `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I've outlined the variables: `tickets`, `searchQuery`, and filters like `statusFilter`. I'm also preparing for form state with items like `newSubject`, `newCategory`, and `newDesc`. I'm adding `selectedTicket` and chat/reply states. I'll need to define how the filters behave, and also handle the enclave simulation. I plan to handle the defaults carefully!\n\n\n**Clarifying Filtering Logic**\n\nI'm now clarifying the filtering logic within `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I've outlined category and linked project filter options. My focus is on ensuring smooth list updates. The ticket filtering logic uses a `filter` array method to determine visibility, as indicated above in the example code, accounting for the `searchQuery`, `statusFilter`, and other filter parameters. I'll need to write this up in code, very soon.\n\n\n**Refining Filtering Strategy**\n\nI'm refining the filtering strategy for `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I've outlined the category and linked project filter implementations. The most recent focus is on handling `selectedTicket` and what should happen if it is removed by filtering. My plan is to show the selected ticket's details regardless, ensuring a smooth display. Now, I'm thinking about edge cases, and will be displaying a clean \"No tickets match your filter parameters\" Empty State when applicable, importing it from `@/components/private-app`. I'm checking the props required to render the `EmptyState` component.\n\n\n**Styling Ticket Display**\n\nI'm now focusing on styling the ticket display within `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I'm planning a bespoke list format. Each ticket will feature an ID badge in a monospace font and the title. Status, Priority, and Category badges are up next. I'll need to use specific colors for the priority levels: critical (red), high (orange), medium (blue), and low (gray). Category badges will be subtly gray, and status badges will use a glowing dot.\n\n\n**Verifying Design Requirements**\n\nI'm now verifying design requirements for the replies display. Each reply will showcase the sender's name, message text, and a cleanly formatted time/date stamp. It should have a secure terminal-based thread appearance. The plan is to include an animated \"handshake\" status inside the ticket details with a system connection status bar like \"LINK SECURED • SOCKET ACTIVE • TRANSIT LOSS: 0.00%\". I've confirmed ticket categories align with the specification. Now, I'm checking mock data and requirements.\n\n\n**Designing Sovereign Operations**\n\nI'm now designing the \"Sovereign Operations Bridge\" console. I'm focusing on the `/app/portal/support/page.tsx` rewrite. I'm planning high-fidelity support statistics like \"active wires\" and \"resolve times.\" The current component can be enhanced. We want to be able to add a preview-created state to a local ticket. I'm also ensuring category, linked project, and status filters are available without backend submission.\n\n\n**Planning Visual Refinements**\n\nI'm now planning visual refinements for `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I envision cryptographic interfaces with strong cues of a secure environment. I'm focusing on visual metaphors such as a high-end grid background, terminal logs, and pulsing connection states. I'm aiming for a dual-column structure, creating a \"Wire Input Enclave\" on the left and the \"Secure Sockets Console\" on the right. I am listing imports I need.\n\n\n**Confirming Component Exports**\n\nI'm checking if `SupportTicket` is exported from `@/components/private-app`, and it is! I just verified `/lib/mock-data-model.ts` exports it. I'm now defining the local `EnrichedSupportTicket` interface. It will expand on the existing data.\n\n\n**Defining Static Constants**\n\nI'm now defining static constants for categories, projects, and priorities within `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I've outlined `CATEGORIES`, `PROJECTS`, and `PRIORITIES` arrays to provide options for filtering and ticket enrichment. Now I'm preparing to enrich existing mock data by incorporating these constants into ticket objects.\n\n```typescript\nconst CATEGORIES = [\n  \"Project Delivery\",\n  \"AI Operations\",\n  \"Billing\",\n  \"Documents\",\n  \"Access\",\n  \"Governance\",\n  \"General\"\n];\n\nconst PROJECTS = [\n  \"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\",\n  \"Model Guardrail Sandbox 04\",\n  \"Sovereign Mining Intel Loop\",\n  \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\",\n  \"General / Non-Project\"\n];\n\nconst PRIORITIES = [\n  \"critical\",\n  \"high\",\n  \"medium\",\n  \"low\"\n];\n```\n\n\n**Drafting Ticket Logic**\n\nI'm now drafting the ticket filtering and display logic for `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I'll implement dynamic statistics that update with real-time ticket interactions. I'll include a simulated telemetry feed within the ticket detail view and ensure a polished design. I'm focusing on perfectly typed code, and checking for formatting dependencies. I'm writing the complete code for `page.tsx` now.\n\n\n**Evaluating Page Routing**\n\nI'm now evaluating page routing for `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`. I think a good approach is to have `/app/portal/support/[id]/page.tsx` as a fallback. It can be a simple mockup that router pushes to the main `/portal/support` page, which handles all interactive work. The current design is spectacular, and I'll list the visual highlights I'm planning to include: interactive backgrounds, premium headers with SVG enclave networks.\n\n\n**Constructing Visual Features**\n\nI'm now integrating visual elements into `/app/portal/support/page.tsx`, specifically those highlights. The SVG grid is incorporated, and I'm designing the SVG network graphic for the header to show enclave connections. I'm planning hover interactions, and a premium call-to-action banner for secure reports. I am preparing the code for `page.tsx`.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:45:50.773Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"adfml7x6","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/portal/support/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport { \n  MessageSquare, Shield, Clock, Users, Send, CheckCircle2, \n  Search, SlidersHorizontal, Plus, ChevronRight, CornerDownRight, \n  RefreshCw, Lock, ArrowUpRight, HelpCircle, HardDrive, ShieldCheck,\n  AlertTriangle, CheckSquare, Sparkles, AlertCircle\n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport { \n  WorkspaceCard, StatusBadge, EmptyState \n} from \"@/components/private-app\";\n\n// ============================================================================\n// Types\n// ============================================================================\ninterface EnrichedSupportTicket {\n  id: string;\n  title: string;\n  status: \"open\" | \"resolved\" | \"in_progress\";\n  priority: \"high\" | \"medium\" | \"low\" | \"critical\";\n  category: \"Project Delivery\" | \"AI Operations\" | \"Billing\" | \"Documents\" | \"Access\" | \"Governance\" | \"General\";\n  linkedProject: string;\n  createdAt: string;\n  desc: string;\n  replies: {\n    sender: string;\n    text: string;\n    timestamp: string;\n  }[];\n}\n\n// ============================================================================\n// Constants\n// ============================================================================\nconst CATEGORIES = [\n  \"Project Delivery\",\n  \"AI Operations\",\n  \"Billing\",\n  \"Documents\",\n  \"Access\",\n  \"Governance\",\n  \"General\"\n] as const;\n\nconst PROJECTS = [\n  \"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\",\n  \"Model Guardrail Sandbox 04\",\n  \"Sovereign Mining Intel Loop\",\n  \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\",\n  \"General / Non-Project\"\n] as const;\n\nconst PRIORITIES = [\n  \"critical\",\n  \"high\",\n  \"medium\",\n  \"low\"\n] as const;\n\nexport default function ClientSupportPage() {\n  // ============================================================================\n  // Initial Mock Data\n  // ============================================================================\n  const [tickets, setTickets] = useState<EnrichedSupportTicket[]>([\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-9912\",\n      title: \"Secure HSM Key Rotation Interlock Delayed\",\n      status: \"open\",\n      priority: \"critical\",\n      category: \"AI Operations\",\n      linkedProject: \"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-27T10:15:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Enclave hardware is reporting socket timeout while performing automatic HSM roll-key rotation with Sovereign Core Sandbox 02. Expected timeout in 45 minutes.\",\n      replies: [\n        {\n          sender: \"Alexander Mercer\",\n          text: \"Initiated automated rotation but the ledger remains uncommitted. Telemetry is fully active.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-27T10:15:00Z\"\n        },\n        {\n          sender: \"Dr. Sarah Vance (Admin)\",\n          text: \"Analyzing cryptographic enclave stream. Standby, we will manually sign the handshake bypass if needed.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-27T10:25:00Z\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-9801\",\n      title: \"Thread Load Allocation Exceeding Normal Boundaries\",\n      status: \"in_progress\",\n      priority: \"high\",\n      category: \"Project Delivery\",\n      linkedProject: \"Model Guardrail Sandbox 04\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-27T07:18:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Node MED-CLINIC-H9 CPU utilization hit 94.5% during diagnostic prompt scan lifecycle. Requesting auto-scaling validation check.\",\n      replies: [\n        {\n          sender: \"Evelyn Carter\",\n          text: \"The threat mapping thread is locked in an infinite evaluation state on local SGX enclave.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-27T07:18:00Z\"\n        },\n        {\n          sender: \"Security Bot\",\n          text: \"Auto-scan activated. Sandboxed namespace isolated. No breach or policy leakage detected.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-27T07:22:00Z\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-9450\",\n      title: \"SOC2 Compliance Report Signoff Complete\",\n      status: \"resolved\",\n      priority: \"medium\",\n      category: \"Governance\",\n      linkedProject: \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-25T11:40:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Audit check complete on all active sandbox namespaces. No policy violations detected across 10,000 epoch transactions.\",\n      replies: [\n        {\n          sender: \"Auditor Jenkins\",\n          text: \"Signed off on compliant enclaves for Q2 2026. Cryptographic seal logged on GFF AI ledger.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-25T11:40:00Z\"\n        },\n        {\n          sender: \"Alexander Mercer\",\n          text: \"Confirmed. Loaded compliance badge into Sovereign Core portal.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-25T14:30:00Z\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-8911\",\n      title: \"Quarterly Audit Vault Verification Interlocked\",\n      status: \"resolved\",\n      priority: \"low\",\n      category: \"Documents\",\n      linkedProject: \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-20T08:00:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Verification check request on HSM archives. The signature ledger requires automatic rollover clearance.\",\n      replies: [\n        {\n          sender: \"Auditor Jenkins\",\n          text: \"Audit ledger hash validated successfully.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-20T08:30:00Z\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-8742\",\n      title: \"SLA Access Elevation Node Bypass\",\n      status: \"in_progress\",\n      priority: \"critical\",\n      category: \"Access\",\n      linkedProject: \"Sovereign Mining Intel Loop\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-18T14:22:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Temporary Level IV Clearance requested for mining thread optimization telemetry validation.\",\n      replies: [\n        {\n          sender: \"Alexander Mercer\",\n          text: \"Requested security clearance elevation for active debugging.\",\n          timestamp: \"2026-06-18T14:25:00Z\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]);\n\n  // ============================================================================\n  // Filter States\n  // ============================================================================\n  const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState(\"\");\n  const [categoryFilter, setCategoryFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n  const [priorityFilter, setPriorityFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n  const [projectFilter, setProjectFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n  const [statusFilter, setStatusFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n\n  // ============================================================================\n  // Create Ticket Form States\n  // ============================================================================\n  const [newSubject, setNewSubject] = useState(\"\");\n  const [newCategory, setNewCategory] = useState<EnrichedSupportTicket[\"category\"]>(\"AI Operations\");\n  const [newPriority, setNewPriority] = useState<EnrichedSupportTicket[\"priority\"]>(\"high\");\n  const [newProject, setNewProject] = useState<string>(\"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\");\n  const [newDesc, setNewDesc] = useState(\"\");\n\n  // ============================================================================\n  // Detail and Interaction States\n  // ============================================================================\n  const [selectedTicketId, setSelectedTicketId] = useState<string>(\"SLA-TKT-9912\");\n  const [replyText, setReplyText] = useState(\"\");\n  const [successToast, setSuccessToast] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  const [syncing, setSyncing] = useState(false);\n  const [showFiltersMobile, setShowFiltersMobile] = useState(false);\n\n  // ============================================================================\n  // Derived / Calculated States\n  // ============================================================================\n  const filteredTickets = tickets.filter(t => {\n    if (searchQuery) {\n      const q = searchQuery.toLowerCase();\n      const matchId = t.id.toLowerCase().includes(q);\n      const matchTitle = t.title.toLowerCase().includes(q);\n      const matchDesc = t.desc.toLowerCase().includes(q);\n      if (!matchId && !matchTitle && !matchDesc) return false;\n    }\n    if (categoryFilter !== \"all\" && t.category !== categoryFilter) return false;\n    if (priorityFilter !== \"all\" && t.priority !== priorityFilter) return false;\n    if (projectFilter !== \"all\" && t.linkedProject !== projectFilter) return false;\n    if (statusFilter !== \"all\" && t.status !== statusFilter) return false;\n    return true;\n  });\n\n  const selectedTicket = tickets.find(t => t.id === selectedTicketId) || filteredTickets[0] || null;\n\n  // Counters\n  const countActive = tickets.filter(t => t.status !== \"resolved\").length;\n  const countResolved = tickets.filter(t => t.status === \"resolved\").length;\n  const countCritical = tickets.filter(t => t.priority === \"critical\" && t.status !== \"resolved\").length;\n  const totalFulfillment = 100; // Guaranteed Enterprise SLA\n\n  // ============================================================================\n  // Handlers\n  // ============================================================================\n  const handleCreateTicket = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!newSubject.trim()) return;\n\n    const tId = `SLA-TKT-${Math.floor(1000 + Math.random() * 9000)}`;\n    const createdTicket: EnrichedSupportTicket = {\n      id: tId,\n      title: newSubject,\n      status: \"open\",\n      priority: newPriority,\n      category: newCategory,\n      linkedProject: newProject,\n      createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n      desc: newDesc || \"No diagnostics telemetry provided.\",\n      replies: [\n        {\n          sender: \"System Handshake\",\n          text: `Secure cryptographic wire established. Routing parameters registered: Priority: ${newPriority.toUpperCase()}, Project: ${newProject}. Connected to GFF Core Systems.`,\n          timestamp: new Date().toISOString()\n        }\n      ]\n    };\n\n    setTickets([createdTicket, ...tickets]);\n    setSelectedTicketId(tId);\n    setNewSubject(\"\");\n    setNewDesc(\"\");\n    \n    // Trigger visual feedback\n    setSuccessToast(`Secure Wire ${tId} Launched`);\n    setTimeout(() => setSuccessToast(null), 4000);\n  };\n\n  const handleSendReply = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!replyText.trim() || !selectedTicket) return;\n\n    const updated = tickets.map(t => {\n      if (t.id === selectedTicket.id) {\n        return {\n          ...t,\n          replies: [\n            ...t.replies,\n            {\n              sender: \"Alexander Mercer (Client)\",\n              text: replyText,\n              timestamp: new Date().toISOString()\n            }\n          ]\n        };\n      }\n      return t;\n    });\n\n    setTickets(updated);\n    setReplyText(\"\");\n\n    // Simulate system diagnostic reply after 2 seconds\n    setSyncing(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      const systemUpdated = updated.map(t => {\n        if (t.id === selectedTicket.id) {\n          return {\n            ...t,\n            replies: [\n              ...t.replies,\n              {\n                sender: \"Sarah Vance (GFF Lead Engineer)\",\n                text: \"Telemetry received and analyzed. Signal verified on cryptographic loop. Restricting memory access boundary temporarily while we execute live validation routines.\",\n                timestamp: new Date().toISOString()\n              }\n            ]\n          };\n        }\n        return t;\n      });\n      setTickets(systemUpdated);\n      setSyncing(false);\n    }, 2000);\n  };\n\n  const getPriorityColor = (p: string) => {\n    switch(p) {\n      case \"critical\": return \"border-red-500/30 text-red-400 bg-red-500/5\";\n      case \"high\": return \"border-amber-500/30 text-amber-400 bg-amber-500/5\";\n      case \"medium\": return \"border-[#009DFF]/30 text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\";\n      default: return \"border-white/10 text-white/55 bg-white/[0.02]\";\n    }\n  };\n\n  const getStatusLabel = (st: string) => {\n    switch (st) {\n      case \"open\": return \"Unresolved\";\n      case \"in_progress\": return \"Evaluating\";\n      case \"resolved\": return \"Sealed\";\n      default: return st;\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-8 relative pb-12\">\n      {/* Premium subtle background grid */}\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.01)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(255,255,255,0.01)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px] pointer-events-none -z-10\" />\n\n      {/* Success Toast */}\n      {successToast && (\n        <div className=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-[#020804] text-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] animate-slide-up\">\n          <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0\" />\n          <div className=\"font-mono text-xs\">\n            <div className=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">{successToast}</div>\n            <div className=\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500/60 mt-0.5\">Encrypted operations tunnel open.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* ============================================================================\n          1. EDITORIAL HERO & SVG ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM\n          ============================================================================ */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col xl:flex-row items-stretch justify-between gap-8 border-b border-white/5 pb-8\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-3xl space-y-4\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse\" />\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n              Secure Operations Wire (SLA Enabled)\n            </span>\n          </div>\n          <h1 className=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono uppercase\">\n            SOVEREIGN CHANNELS\n          </h1>\n          <p className=\"text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed font-mono\">\n            Cryptographically isolated, zero-trust support wires linking approved client operators directly to core GFF Systems Engineers. All operations logs are hardware-enclaved, SOC2 audited, and bound by strict cryptographic SLA performance targets.\n          </p>\n          \n          <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-1\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n              <Lock className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n              <span>AES-256 HSM Handshake</span>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n              <Shield className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <span>Dual-Operator Approval Locks</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* High-fidelity SVG handshake graphic */}\n        <div className=\"hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm relative overflow-hidden select-none w-full xl:w-[420px] shrink-0\">\n          <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-radial-gradient from-blue-500/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none\" />\n          <svg width=\"340\" height=\"110\" viewBox=\"0 0 340 110\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" className=\"font-mono text-[9px] uppercase\">\n            {/* Grid background inside SVG */}\n            <defs>\n              <pattern id=\"inner-grid\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n                <path d=\"M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.01)\" strokeWidth=\"0.5\"/>\n              </pattern>\n            </defs>\n            <rect width=\"340\" height=\"110\" fill=\"url(#inner-grid)\" />\n            \n            {/* Connection line */}\n            <path d=\"M 60 55 L 280 55\" stroke=\"rgba(0, 157, 255, 0.2)\" strokeWidth=\"1\" strokeDasharray=\"4 4\" />\n            <path d=\"M 60 55 L 170 20 L 280 55\" stroke=\"rgba(0, 255, 194, 0.15)\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            \n            {/* Node 1: Client Enclave */}\n            <circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"55\" r=\"16\" fill=\"#030303\" stroke=\"#009DFF\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            <circle cx=\"60\" cy=\"55\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#009DFF\" />\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"85\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fontWeight=\"bold\">Client Node</text>\n            <text x=\"30\" y=\"95\" fill=\"#009DFF\" textAnchor=\"middle\">0xAM_SEC</text>\n\n            {/* Node 2: Core systems bridge */}\n            <circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"20\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#030303\" stroke=\"#00FFC2\" strokeWidth=\"1\" />\n            <circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#00FFC2\" className=\"animate-pulse\" />\n            <text x=\"170\" y=\"10\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fontWeight=\"bold\">SLA Bridge</text>\n\n            {/* Node 3: GFF Core */}\n            <circle cx=\"280\" cy=\"55\" r=\"16\" fill=\"#030303\" stroke=\"#00FFC2\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" />\n            <circle cx=\"280\" cy=\"55\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#00FFC2\" />\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"85\" fill=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)\" textAnchor=\"middle\" fontWeight=\"bold\">GFF Core</text>\n            <text x=\"310\" y=\"95\" fill=\"#00FFC2\" textAnchor=\"middle\">Sarah_V</text>\n\n            {/* Animated data packet */}\n            <circle cx=\"140\" cy=\"55\" r=\"2\" fill=\"#00FFC2\">\n              <animate attributeName=\"cx\" values=\"60;280;60\" dur=\"8s\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\" />\n            </circle>\n          </svg>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ============================================================================\n          2. OPERATIONAL TELEMETRY BENTO CARD GRID (STAT CARDS)\n          ============================================================================ */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-28 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 hover:border-white/10 transition-all p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">Active Sockets</span>\n          <div className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] mt-1\">\n            {countActive} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">WIRES</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 mt-1\">\n            <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n            <span>Telemetry loops active</span>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-28 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 hover:border-white/10 transition-all p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">Mean Resolve Time</span>\n          <div className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-white mt-1\">\n            9.4 <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">MIN</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono text-green-400 mt-1\">\n            <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400\" />\n            <span>Target response: &lt;15m</span>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-28 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 hover:border-white/10 transition-all p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">Critical Escalations</span>\n          <div className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-amber-400 mt-1\">\n            {countCritical} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">OPEN</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 mt-1\">\n            <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-amber-400\" />\n            <span>Hardware interlocks checked</span>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-28 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 hover:border-white/10 transition-all p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">SLA Adherence</span>\n          <div className=\"text-3xl font-mono font-bold text-[#00FFC2] mt-1\">\n            {totalFulfillment}% <span className=\"text-xs text-white/30 font-normal\">PERFECT</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[9px] font-mono text-[#00FFC2] mt-1\">\n            <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n            <span>100% compliant security model</span>\n          </div>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ============================================================================\n          3. CONTROLS / FILTER BAR\n          ============================================================================ */}\n      <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-3\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 items-stretch md:items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"relative flex-grow max-w-xl\">\n            <Search className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 w-4 h-4 text-white/30\" />\n            <input \n              type=\"text\" \n              value={searchQuery} \n              onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)} \n              placeholder=\"Search secure wires by subject, body text, or SLA-TKT hash ID...\"\n              className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] pl-9 pr-8 text-xs font-mono text-white placeholder-white/30 outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/35 focus:bg-white/[0.02] transition-all\"\n            />\n            {searchQuery && (\n              <button \n                onClick={() => setSearchQuery(\"\")} \n                className=\"absolute right-3 top-2.5 text-white/40 hover:text-white\"\n              >\n                ×\n              </button>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <button\n              onClick={() => setShowFiltersMobile(!showFiltersMobile)}\n              className=\"md:hidden flex h-9 px-3 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-xs font-mono text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all\"\n            >\n              <SlidersHorizontal className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              <span>Filters</span>\n            </button>\n            <button\n              onClick={() => {\n                setSearchQuery(\"\");\n                setCategoryFilter(\"all\");\n                setPriorityFilter(\"all\");\n                setProjectFilter(\"all\");\n                setStatusFilter(\"all\");\n              }}\n              className=\"flex h-9 px-3 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-xs font-mono text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n              title=\"Reset Filters\"\n            >\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n              <span className=\"hidden sm:inline\">Reset</span>\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Filters Panel (Shown always on md+, state-controlled on mobile) */}\n        <div className={`${showFiltersMobile ? \"block\" : \"hidden\"} md:block grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 pt-2 border-t border-white/[0.03]`}>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">Category</label>\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select \n                value={categoryFilter} \n                onChange={(e) => setCategoryFilter(e.target.value)} \n                className=\"w-full h-8.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-2.5 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"all\">ALL CATEGORIES</option>\n                {CATEGORIES.map(cat => <option key={cat} value={cat}>{cat}</option>)}\n              </select>\n              <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-2.5 top-2.5 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">SLA Priority</label>\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select \n                value={priorityFilter} \n                onChange={(e) => setPriorityFilter(e.target.value)} \n                className=\"w-full h-8.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-2.5 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"all\">ALL PRIORITIES</option>\n                {PRIORITIES.map(prio => <option key={prio} value={prio}>{prio.toUpperCase()}</option>)}\n              </select>\n              <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-2.5 top-2.5 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">Linked Project</label>\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select \n                value={projectFilter} \n                onChange={(e) => setProjectFilter(e.target.value)} \n                className=\"w-full h-8.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-2.5 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"all\">ALL PROJECTS</option>\n                {PROJECTS.map(proj => <option key={proj} value={proj}>{proj}</option>)}\n              </select>\n              <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-2.5 top-2.5 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">Operational Status</label>\n            <div className=\"relative\">\n              <select \n                value={statusFilter} \n                onChange={(e) => setStatusFilter(e.target.value)} \n                className=\"w-full h-8.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] px-2.5 pr-8 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n              >\n                <option value=\"all\">ALL STATUSES</option>\n                <option value=\"open\">UNRESOLVED</option>\n                <option value=\"in_progress\">EVALUATING</option>\n                <option value=\"resolved\">SEALED (RESOLVED)</option>\n              </select>\n              <SlidersHorizontal className=\"absolute right-2.5 top-2.5 w-3 h-3 text-white/30 pointer-events-none\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ============================================================================\n          4. MAIN CONTAINER: CREATE FORM & TICKETS GRID / DETAILS\n          ============================================================================ */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\">\n        \n        {/* LEFT COLUMN: Launch Wire Form (col-span-4) */}\n        <div className=\"xl:col-span-4 space-y-6\">\n          <WorkspaceCard className=\"p-5 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-5\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <MessageSquare className=\"w-5 h-5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                Initiate New Secure Wire\n              </h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <form onSubmit={handleCreateTicket} className=\"space-y-4\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold tracking-wider\">Ticket Subject</label>\n                <input\n                  required\n                  type=\"text\"\n                  placeholder=\"e.g., Replication delay in Node A enclave\"\n                  value={newSubject}\n                  onChange={e => setNewSubject(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-3 text-white text-[12px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 transition-all\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold tracking-wider\">Category</label>\n                  <select\n                    value={newCategory}\n                    onChange={e => setNewCategory(e.target.value as EnrichedSupportTicket[\"category\"])}\n                    className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-2 text-white text-[11px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                  >\n                    {CATEGORIES.map(cat => (\n                      <option key={cat} value={cat} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">{cat}</option>\n                    ))}\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold tracking-wider\">SLA Priority</label>\n                  <select\n                    value={newPriority}\n                    onChange={e => setNewPriority(e.target.value as EnrichedSupportTicket[\"priority\"])}\n                    className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-2 text-white text-[11px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                  >\n                    <option value=\"low\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">Low</option>\n                    <option value=\"medium\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">Medium</option>\n                    <option value=\"high\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">High</option>\n                    <option value=\"critical\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">Critical</option>\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold tracking-wider\">Linked Project Namespace</label>\n                <select\n                  value={newProject}\n                  onChange={e => setNewProject(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-2.5 text-white text-[11px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 cursor-pointer appearance-none uppercase\"\n                >\n                  {PROJECTS.map(proj => (\n                    <option key={proj} value={proj} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">{proj}</option>\n                  ))}\n                </select>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n                <label className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold tracking-wider\">Telemetry Logs / Diagnostics</label>\n                <textarea\n                  required\n                  placeholder=\"Paste secure enclave log payloads or diagnostic traces here. (e.g. Socket exception at 0x7FFA...)\"\n                  value={newDesc}\n                  onChange={e => setNewDesc(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-28 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 p-3 text-white text-[12px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 resize-none transition-all\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <button \n                type=\"submit\" \n                className=\"w-full h-10 rounded-lg bg-white hover:bg-white/90 text-black font-mono font-bold text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.05)] active:scale-[0.98]\"\n              >\n                Establish Secure Wire\n              </button>\n            </form>\n          </WorkspaceCard>\n\n          {/* SLA Security Warning Box */}\n          <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-yellow-500/10 bg-yellow-500/[0.02] text-[11px] font-mono text-yellow-500/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-3\">\n            <AlertTriangle className=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0 text-yellow-500/90\" />\n            <div>\n              <span className=\"font-bold text-yellow-500 uppercase block mb-1\">Dual Operator Check Required</span>\n              Action commands transmitted through this socket execute core boundary adaptations. Logs are shared directly with sovereign auditors. Use caution.\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* RIGHT COLUMN: Tickets Grid & Details Panel (col-span-8) */}\n        <div className=\"xl:col-span-8 space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6\">\n            \n            {/* Tickets List View (5 cols) */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 space-y-3 max-h-[640px] overflow-y-auto pr-1\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between px-1\">\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">\n                  Secure Sockets\n                </span>\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1.5 py-0.2 rounded font-bold\">\n                  {filteredTickets.length} / {tickets.length} Wires\n                </span>\n              </div>\n\n              {filteredTickets.length === 0 ? (\n                <EmptyState\n                  title=\"No Sockets Open\"\n                  description=\"No secure wires match your query.\"\n                  actionLabel=\"Reset Search Constraints\"\n                  onAction={() => {\n                    setSearchQuery(\"\");\n                    setCategoryFilter(\"all\");\n                    setPriorityFilter(\"all\");\n                    setProjectFilter(\"all\");\n                    setStatusFilter(\"all\");\n                  }}\n                />\n              ) : (\n                <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  {filteredTickets.map(ticket => {\n                    const isSelected = selectedTicket && selectedTicket.id === ticket.id;\n                    const isCrit = ticket.priority === \"critical\";\n                    const isOpen = ticket.status === \"open\";\n                    \n                    return (\n                      <div\n                        key={ticket.id}\n                        onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(ticket.id)}\n                        className={`group relative p-3.5 rounded-xl border transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer select-none text-left ${\n                          isSelected \n                            ? \"bg-[#0b1424]/30 border-[#009DFF]/40 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.05)]\" \n                            : \"bg-[#050505]/40 border-white/5 hover:border-white/10\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {/* Selected accent bar */}\n                        {isSelected && (\n                          <div className=\"absolute left-0 top-3 bottom-3 w-1.5 rounded-r-lg bg-[#009DFF]\" />\n                        )}\n\n                        <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono\">\n                            <span className=\"text-white/35 font-bold tracking-wider\">{ticket.id}</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white/40\">\n                              {new Date(ticket.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n\n                          <h4 className={`text-[12px] font-bold font-mono tracking-tight line-clamp-1 transition-colors ${\n                            isSelected ? \"text-white\" : \"text-white/80 group-hover:text-white\"\n                          }`}>\n                            {ticket.title}\n                          </h4>\n\n                          <div className=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 pt-1\">\n                            {/* Priority Badge */}\n                            <span className={`px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[8.5px] font-mono font-bold uppercase border ${getPriorityColor(ticket.priority)}`}>\n                              {ticket.priority}\n                            </span>\n                            \n                            {/* Category Badge */}\n                            <span className=\"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-[8.5px] font-mono text-white/50 bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/5 uppercase\">\n                              {ticket.category}\n                            </span>\n\n                            {/* Status Bullet */}\n                            <div className=\"ml-auto flex items-center gap-1\">\n                              <span className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${\n                                ticket.status === \"resolved\" ? \"bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_6px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)]\" :\n                                ticket.status === \"in_progress\" ? \"bg-blue-400 shadow-[0_0_6px_rgba(0,157,255,0.5)]\" :\n                                \"bg-amber-400 shadow-[0_0_6px_rgba(251,191,36,0.5)] animate-pulse\"\n                              }`} />\n                              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase\">\n                                {getStatusLabel(ticket.status)}\n                              </span>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Conversation/Thread Hub Panel (7 cols) */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-7\">\n              {selectedTicket ? (\n                <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full min-h-[500px]\">\n                  \n                  {/* Thread Header */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] flex items-center justify-between gap-4 font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                        <span className=\"text-xs font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">{selectedTicket.id}</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/20\">•</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold\">{selectedTicket.category}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <h3 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight line-clamp-1\">\n                        {selectedTicket.title}\n                      </h3>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"shrink-0 text-right\">\n                      {/* Interactive Change Status button for preview */}\n                      <button \n                        onClick={() => {\n                          const updated = tickets.map(t => {\n                            if (t.id === selectedTicket.id) {\n                              const nextStatus = t.status === \"open\" ? \"in_progress\" : t.status === \"in_progress\" ? \"resolved\" : \"open\";\n                              return { ...t, status: nextStatus };\n                            }\n                            return t;\n                          });\n                          setTickets(updated);\n                        }}\n                        className=\"px-2 py-1 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all flex items-center gap-1.5\"\n                        title=\"Toggle status cycle for preview\"\n                      >\n                        <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                        <span>Cycle Status</span>\n                      </button>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Operational Telemetry Sub-panel */}\n                  <div className=\"p-3 bg-[#020202]/60 border-b border-white/5 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2.5 font-mono text-[9.5px]\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold\">Priority Bounds:</span>\n                      <div className=\"text-white font-bold uppercase flex items-center gap-1\">\n                        <span className={`w-1 h-3 rounded ${\n                          selectedTicket.priority === \"critical\" ? \"bg-red-500\" :\n                          selectedTicket.priority === \"high\" ? \"bg-amber-400\" : \"bg-[#009DFF]\"\n                        }`} />\n                        {selectedTicket.priority.toUpperCase()}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold\">Target Enclave:</span>\n                      <div className=\"text-white font-bold truncate max-w-[130px]\" title={selectedTicket.linkedProject}>\n                        {selectedTicket.linkedProject}\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5 col-span-2 sm:col-span-1\">\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 uppercase font-semibold\">Session Status:</span>\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">\n                        <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FFC2] animate-pulse\" />\n                        <span>SOCKET SECURED</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Initial description log */}\n                  <div className=\"p-4 bg-black/40 border-b border-white/5 space-y-1.5 text-left font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/35 text-[9px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest block\">\n                      Enclave Diagnostics Payload\n                    </span>\n                    <div className=\"p-3 rounded bg-[#020202] border border-white/5 text-white/80 select-text overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap max-h-[120px]\">\n                      {selectedTicket.desc}\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Conversation feed */}\n                  <div className=\"flex-grow p-4 space-y-4 max-h-[280px] overflow-y-auto bg-[#020202]/30 text-left\">\n                    <div className=\"text-center\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold\">\n                        — Secure Wire Session Initialized —\n                      </span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {selectedTicket.replies.map((reply, index) => {\n                      const isClient = reply.sender.includes(\"Alexander\") || reply.sender.includes(\"Client\") || reply.sender.includes(\"Evelyn\");\n                      const isSystem = reply.sender.includes(\"System\");\n                      \n                      return (\n                        <div key={index} className=\"space-y-1\">\n                          <div className={`flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-mono ${\n                            isClient ? \"justify-end text-[#009DFF]\" : isSystem ? \"justify-center text-white/30\" : \"justify-start text-[#00FFC2]\"\n                          }`}>\n                            <span className=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">{reply.sender}</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white/20\">•</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/45\">\n                              {new Date(reply.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' })}\n                            </span>\n                          </div>\n\n                          <div className={`flex ${isClient ? \"justify-end\" : isSystem ? \"justify-center\" : \"justify-start\"}`}>\n                            <div className={`max-w-[85%] rounded-lg px-3.5 py-2 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed select-text ${\n                              isSystem\n                                ? \"bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 text-white/40 text-center\"\n                                : isClient\n                                  ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/25 text-white/95 text-right\"\n                                  : \"bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/20 text-white/95 text-left\"\n                            }`}>\n                              {reply.text}\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      );\n                    })}\n\n                    {/* Simulating engineering feedback loader */}\n                    {syncing && (\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[10.5px] font-mono text-white/40\">\n                        <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-spin text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                        <span>Core engineer routing encryption handshake...</span>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Live Feed Input Reply Box */}\n                  <form onSubmit={handleSendReply} className=\"p-3 border-t border-white/5 bg-black/[0.2] flex gap-2\">\n                    <input\n                      type=\"text\"\n                      placeholder={selectedTicket.status === \"resolved\" ? \"This socket is sealed. Toggle Cycle Status to reopen.\" : \"Transmit reply over secured enclave...\"}\n                      disabled={selectedTicket.status === \"resolved\"}\n                      value={replyText}\n                      onChange={e => setReplyText(e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"flex-grow h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-3 text-white text-[12px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\"\n                    />\n                    <button\n                      type=\"submit\"\n                      disabled={!replyText.trim() || selectedTicket.status === \"resolved\"}\n                      className=\"h-9 w-9 rounded-lg bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] disabled:bg-white/5 disabled:text-white/20 text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,157,255,0.2)] disabled:shadow-none shrink-0\"\n                    >\n                      <Send className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                    </button>\n                  </form>\n\n                </div>\n              ) : (\n                <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 text-center min-h-[400px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-3\">\n                  <HelpCircle className=\"w-12 h-12 text-white/20\" />\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40 font-mono text-xs uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">\n                    No Socket Selected\n                  </span>\n                  <p className=\"text-white/30 text-xs font-mono max-w-sm\">\n                    Select an active socket from the left panel to inspect parameters and communicate over secure wires.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ============================================================================\n          5. PREMIUM CTA SECTION (SLA PERFORMANCE VERIFICATION)\n          ============================================================================ */}\n      <WorkspaceCard className=\"border border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#040914] to-[#010307] p-6 space-y-4 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n        <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 pointer-events-none\">\n          <ShieldCheck className=\"w-48 h-48 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-2 max-w-3xl font-mono\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[#009DFF]\">\n              <ShieldCheck className=\"w-5 h-5 animate-pulse\" />\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">Emergency System Override Protocol</span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-[16px] font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight\">Need immediate physical hardware decoupling?</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n              If you detect boundary containment failure or keys leakage, authorized Level IV security managers can request instant memory core isolation or enclave decoupling. These critical commands are routed under high-priority hardware SLA loops with immediate execution verification.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"shrink-0 font-mono\">\n            <button \n              onClick={() => {\n                setSuccessToast(\"Emergency Handshake Broadcasted\");\n                setTimeout(() => setSuccessToast(null), 4000);\n              }}\n              className=\"inline-flex h-10 px-5 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-wider transition-all hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(239,68,68,0.4)] active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer\"\n            >\n              Request Core Decoupling\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </WorkspaceCard>\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
