{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:46:56.264Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Refining File Handling**\n\nI've hit a snag with the editor; large text is causing issues. The current plan is to handle file creation and content replacement in smaller segments, especially if the file already exists. I think chunking will solve this, but I am exploring other approaches, too.\n\n\n**Exploring File Writing Strategies**\n\nI've hit a roadblock with the `editor` due to the code's size, which is around 25,000 characters. Replacing the entire `page.tsx` file directly fails because the editor input limit. I'm now exploring alternatives. My initial thought is to use `run_commands` and leverage a Python or Node inline script or heredoc to write the file, or use the editor in smaller chunks to bypass the limits. The `run_commands` tool seems promising for this non-interactive file writing task.\n\n\n**Confirming Python File Writing**\n\nI'm now fully committed to a Python-based solution using `run_commands` to write the `/app/portal/support/page.tsx` file. A Python script can write any file size without truncation, sidestepping editor limitations. The speed and reliability are excellent. I'm currently crafting the precise Python command, including careful escaping, to ensure seamless execution. I'll construct the script as a multiline string within the Python command and confirm it's valid.\n\n\n**Evaluating Node.js Approach**\n\nOkay, I'm pivoting back towards a Node.js solution. It occurred to me that Node is readily available, making a dedicated Python script unnecessary. I'm exploring writing a temporary `write_page.js` script with the React code. However, the `new_text` for the script itself might still exceed the editor's limits. I'm recalling the editor size limits; writing small chunks seems to be the key to success.\n\n\n**Revisiting File Editing Limits**\n\nI'm back to considering chunking the file writing. The existing `page.tsx` is only 6,700 characters, so the editor limits might not be the issue, as I initially thought. I am wondering if I could just directly edit the existing file. I'm exploring writing a shell command using a heredoc or using python with base64 for elegant and simple encoding, and if that works to resolve character limitations I'll give it a shot.\n\n\n**Implementing Chunked File Writes**\n\nI've decided to employ the `editor` in a chunked manner, which I think will be much simpler. My current plan involves replacing the entire file with a skeleton file that is only around 10 lines of imports, then appending the rest of the file in chunks using `insert_line` one by one. I am confirming that the target file has 135 lines. I'm hopeful this method circumvents any character limits.\n\n\n**Refining File Replacement**\n\nI'm now focusing on a direct `cat` command approach via `run_commands`. This seems the simplest path. I considered, but rejected, chunked appends. I am concerned with the `run_commands` 12,000 character limit. Breaking the file into chunks, with a modular skeleton, may solve the problem. I'm prioritizing direct replacement via the shell, which will be the easiest.\n\n\n\n**Optimizing File Content**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on code optimization to reduce file size. I realize the initial bloat stems from descriptive text, a large SVG diagram, mock data structures, and comments. My goal is to make the code fit within the 12,000 character limit of `run_commands`. I'm rewriting the inline SVG using Lucide icons and CSS for a cleaner, more compact visual, which saves significant space. Additionally, I'm compressing the mock data by shortening some detailed text while retaining technical accuracy.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:46:56.269Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"93t6o6oy","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/portal/support/page.tsx","old_text":null,"new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState } from \"react\";\nimport { \n  MessageSquare, Shield, Clock, Send, CheckCircle2, \n  Search, SlidersHorizontal, RefreshCw, Lock, ShieldCheck,\n  AlertTriangle, HelpCircle, HardDrive\n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport { \n  WorkspaceCard, EmptyState \n} from \"@/components/private-app\";\n\ninterface EnrichedSupportTicket {\n  id: string;\n  title: string;\n  status: \"open\" | \"resolved\" | \"in_progress\";\n  priority: \"high\" | \"medium\" | \"low\" | \"critical\";\n  category: \"Project Delivery\" | \"AI Operations\" | \"Billing\" | \"Documents\" | \"Access\" | \"Governance\" | \"General\";\n  linkedProject: string;\n  createdAt: string;\n  desc: string;\n  replies: {\n    sender: string;\n    text: string;\n    timestamp: string;\n  }[];\n}\n\nconst CATEGORIES = [\"Project Delivery\", \"AI Operations\", \"Billing\", \"Documents\", \"Access\", \"Governance\", \"General\"] as const;\nconst PROJECTS = [\"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\", \"Model Guardrail Sandbox 04\", \"Sovereign Mining Intel Loop\", \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\", \"General / Non-Project\"] as const;\nconst PRIORITIES = [\"critical\", \"high\", \"medium\", \"low\"] as const;\n\nexport default function ClientSupportPage() {\n  const [tickets, setTickets] = useState<EnrichedSupportTicket[]>([\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-9912\",\n      title: \"Secure HSM Key Rotation Interlock Delayed\",\n      status: \"open\",\n      priority: \"critical\",\n      category: \"AI Operations\",\n      linkedProject: \"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-27T10:15:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Enclave hardware is reporting socket timeout while performing automatic HSM roll-key rotation with Sovereign Core Sandbox 02. Expected timeout in 45 minutes.\",\n      replies: [\n        { sender: \"Alexander Mercer\", text: \"Initiated automated rotation but the ledger remains uncommitted. Telemetry is active.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-27T10:15:00Z\" },\n        { sender: \"Dr. Sarah Vance (Admin)\", text: \"Analyzing cryptographic enclave stream. Standby, we will manually sign the handshake bypass if needed.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-27T10:25:00Z\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-9801\",\n      title: \"Thread Load Allocation Exceeding Normal Boundaries\",\n      status: \"in_progress\",\n      priority: \"high\",\n      category: \"Project Delivery\",\n      linkedProject: \"Model Guardrail Sandbox 04\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-27T07:18:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Node MED-CLINIC-H9 CPU utilization hit 94.5% during diagnostic prompt scan lifecycle. Requesting auto-scaling validation check.\",\n      replies: [\n        { sender: \"Evelyn Carter\", text: \"The threat mapping thread is locked in an infinite evaluation state on local SGX enclave.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-27T07:18:00Z\" },\n        { sender: \"Security Bot\", text: \"Auto-scan activated. Sandboxed namespace isolated. No breach detected.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-27T07:22:00Z\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-9450\",\n      title: \"SOC2 Compliance Report Signoff Complete\",\n      status: \"resolved\",\n      priority: \"medium\",\n      category: \"Governance\",\n      linkedProject: \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-25T11:40:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Audit check complete on all active sandbox namespaces. No policy violations detected across 10,000 epoch transactions.\",\n      replies: [\n        { sender: \"Auditor Jenkins\", text: \"Signed off on compliant enclaves for Q2 2026. Cryptographic seal logged on GFF AI ledger.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-25T11:40:00Z\" },\n        { sender: \"Alexander Mercer\", text: \"Confirmed. Loaded compliance badge into Sovereign Core portal.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-25T14:30:00Z\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-8911\",\n      title: \"Quarterly Audit Vault Verification Interlocked\",\n      status: \"resolved\",\n      priority: \"low\",\n      category: \"Documents\",\n      linkedProject: \"Federal Ledger Enclave Alpha\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-20T08:00:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Verification check request on HSM archives. The signature ledger requires automatic rollover clearance.\",\n      replies: [\n        { sender: \"Auditor Jenkins\", text: \"Audit ledger hash validated successfully.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-20T08:30:00Z\" }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"SLA-TKT-8742\",\n      title: \"SLA Access Elevation Node Bypass\",\n      status: \"in_progress\",\n      priority: \"critical\",\n      category: \"Access\",\n      linkedProject: \"Sovereign Mining Intel Loop\",\n      createdAt: \"2026-06-18T14:22:00Z\",\n      desc: \"Temporary Level IV Clearance requested for mining thread optimization telemetry validation.\",\n      replies: [\n        { sender: \"Alexander Mercer\", text: \"Requested security clearance elevation for active debugging.\", timestamp: \"2026-06-18T14:25:00Z\" }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]);\n\n  const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState(\"\");\n  const [categoryFilter, setCategoryFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n  const [priorityFilter, setPriorityFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n  const [projectFilter, setProjectFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n  const [statusFilter, setStatusFilter] = useState<string>(\"all\");\n\n  const [newSubject, setNewSubject] = useState(\"\");\n  const [newCategory, setNewCategory] = useState<EnrichedSupportTicket[\"category\"]>(\"AI Operations\");\n  const [newPriority, setNewPriority] = useState<EnrichedSupportTicket[\"priority\"]>(\"high\");\n  const [newProject, setNewProject] = useState<string>(\"Sovereign Core Sandbox 02\");\n  const [newDesc, setNewDesc] = useState(\"\");\n\n  const [selectedTicketId, setSelectedTicketId] = useState<string>(\"SLA-TKT-9912\");\n  const [replyText, setReplyText] = useState(\"\");\n  const [successToast, setSuccessToast] = useState<string | null>(null);\n  const [syncing, setSyncing] = useState(false);\n  const [showFiltersMobile, setShowFiltersMobile] = useState(false);\n\n  const filteredTickets = tickets.filter(t => {\n    if (searchQuery) {\n      const q = searchQuery.toLowerCase();\n      if (!t.id.toLowerCase().includes(q) && !t.title.toLowerCase().includes(q) && !t.desc.toLowerCase().includes(q)) return false;\n    }\n    if (categoryFilter !== \"all\" && t.category !== categoryFilter) return false;\n    if (priorityFilter !== \"all\" && t.priority !== priorityFilter) return false;\n    if (projectFilter !== \"all\" && t.linkedProject !== projectFilter) return false;\n    if (statusFilter !== \"all\" && t.status !== statusFilter) return false;\n    return true;\n  });\n\n  const selectedTicket = tickets.find(t => t.id === selectedTicketId) || filteredTickets[0] || null;\n\n  const countActive = tickets.filter(t => t.status !== \"resolved\").length;\n  const countResolved = tickets.filter(t => t.status === \"resolved\").length;\n  const countCritical = tickets.filter(t => t.priority === \"critical\" && t.status !== \"resolved\").length;\n\n  const handleCreateTicket = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!newSubject.trim()) return;\n\n    const tId = `SLA-TKT-${Math.floor(1000 + Math.random() * 9000)}`;\n    const createdTicket: EnrichedSupportTicket = {\n      id: tId,\n      title: newSubject,\n      status: \"open\",\n      priority: newPriority,\n      category: newCategory,\n      linkedProject: newProject,\n      createdAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n      desc: newDesc || \"No diagnostics telemetry provided.\",\n      replies: [\n        { sender: \"System Handshake\", text: `Secure wire established. Priority: ${newPriority.toUpperCase()}, Project: ${newProject}.`, timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }\n      ]\n    };\n\n    setTickets([createdTicket, ...tickets]);\n    setSelectedTicketId(tId);\n    setNewSubject(\"\");\n    setNewDesc(\"\");\n    setSuccessToast(`Secure Wire ${tId} Launched`);\n    setTimeout(() => setSuccessToast(null), 4000);\n  };\n\n  const handleSendReply = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    if (!replyText.trim() || !selectedTicket) return;\n\n    const updated = tickets.map(t => {\n      if (t.id === selectedTicket.id) {\n        return {\n          ...t,\n          replies: [...t.replies, { sender: \"Alexander Mercer (Client)\", text: replyText, timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }]\n        };\n      }\n      return t;\n    });\n\n    setTickets(updated);\n    setReplyText(\"\");\n    setSyncing(true);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      const systemUpdated = updated.map(t => {\n        if (t.id === selectedTicket.id) {\n          return {\n            ...t,\n            replies: [...t.replies, { sender: \"Sarah Vance (GFF Lead)\", text: \"Telemetry received. Analyzing cryptographically sandboxed namespaces. Standby.\", timestamp: new Date().toISOString() }]\n          };\n        }\n        return t;\n      });\n      setTickets(systemUpdated);\n      setSyncing(false);\n    }, 1800);\n  };\n\n  const getPriorityColor = (p: string) => {\n    switch(p) {\n      case \"critical\": return \"border-red-500/30 text-red-400 bg-red-500/5\";\n      case \"high\": return \"border-amber-500/30 text-amber-400 bg-amber-500/5\";\n      case \"medium\": return \"border-[#009DFF]/30 text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5\";\n      default: return \"border-white/10 text-white/50 bg-white/[0.02]\";\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 relative pb-12\">\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(255,255,255,0.01)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,rgba(255,255,255,0.01)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px] pointer-events-none -z-10\" />\n\n      {successToast && (\n        <div className=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-[#020804] text-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(16,185,129,0.15)] animate-slide-up\">\n          <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-5 h-5 shrink-0\" />\n          <div className=\"font-mono text-xs\">\n            <div className=\"font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">{successToast}</div>\n            <div className=\"text-[10px] text-emerald-500/60 mt-0.5\">Encrypted tunnel established.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* 1. EDITORIAL HEADER */}\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start justify-between gap-6 border-b border-white/5 pb-6\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-3xl space-y-3\">\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 animate-pulse\" />\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">Secure Support Wire</span>\n          </div>\n          <h1 className=\"text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight font-mono uppercase\">SOVEREIGN CHANNELS</h1>\n          <p className=\"text-xs md:text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-mono\">\n            Cryptographically isolated operations channels. Core GFF Systems Engineers are actively listening on dual-layer hardware enclaves for authorized operators.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* CSS/SVG Handshake Graphic */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm shrink-0 w-full lg:w-auto font-mono text-[10px] text-white/45\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col\">\n            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">CLIENT NODE</span>\n            <span>0xAM_SEC</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"h-0.5 w-10 border-t border-dashed border-white/20 relative\">\n            <span className=\"absolute -top-1 left-4 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FFC2] animate-ping\" />\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col text-center\">\n            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">SLA BRIDGE</span>\n            <span className=\"text-emerald-400 text-[8px]\">ACTIVE</span>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"h-0.5 w-10 border-t border-dashed border-white/20\" />\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col text-right\">\n            <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/55 font-bold\">GFF CORE</span>\n            <span>Sarah_V</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 2. OPERATIONAL BENTO GRID */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4\">\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-24 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">Active Sockets</span>\n          <div className=\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">{countActive} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/20 font-normal\">WIRES</span></div>\n          <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/40\">Telemetry locks engaged</span>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-24 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">Mean Resolve Time</span>\n          <div className=\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white\">9.4 <span className=\"text-xs text-white/20 font-normal\">MIN</span></div>\n          <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-green-400\">Target Response: &lt;15m</span>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-24 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">Critical Escalations</span>\n          <div className=\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-amber-400\">{countCritical} <span className=\"text-xs text-white/20 font-normal\">OPEN</span></div>\n          <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/40\">Hardware interlocks active</span>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n        <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col justify-between h-24 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/20 p-4\">\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-white/35\">SLA Adherence</span>\n          <div className=\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-[#00FFC2]\">100% <span className=\"text-xs text-white/20 font-normal\">PERFECT</span></div>\n          <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-[#00FFC2]\">SOC2 compliant security</span>\n        </WorkspaceCard>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 3. CONTROLS BAR */}\n      <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-3\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 items-stretch md:items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"relative flex-grow max-w-xl\">\n            <Search className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/30\" />\n            <input \n              type=\"text\" \n              value={searchQuery} \n              onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)} \n              placeholder=\"Filter secure wires by subject or content...\"\n              className=\"w-full h-8.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] pl-8.5 pr-8 text-xs font-mono text-white placeholder-white/30 outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/35 focus:bg-white/[0.02] transition-all\"\n            />\n            {searchQuery && <button onClick={() => setSearchQuery(\"\")} className=\"absolute right-3 top-2.5 text-white/40 hover:text-white text-xs\">×</button>}\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <button\n              onClick={() => setShowFiltersMobile(!showFiltersMobile)}\n              className=\"md:hidden flex h-8.5 px-3 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] text-xs font-mono text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all\"\n            >\n              <SlidersHorizontal className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n              <span>Filters</span>\n            </button>\n            <button\n              onClick={() => {\n                setSearchQuery(\"\");\n                setCategoryFilter(\"all\");\n                setPriorityFilter(\"all\");\n                setProjectFilter(\"all\");\n                setStatusFilter(\"all\");\n              }}\n              className=\"flex h-8.5 px-3 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-xs font-mono text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n            >\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n              <span>Reset</span>\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Filters Panel */}\n        <div className={`${showFiltersMobile ? \"block\" : \"hidden\"} md:block grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 pt-2 border-t border-white/[0.03]`}>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">Category</label>\n            <select value={categoryFilter} onChange={(e) => setCategoryFilter(e.target.value)} className=\"w-full h-8 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0c0c0c] px-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\">\n              <option value=\"all\">ALL CATEGORIES</option>\n              {CATEGORIES.map(cat => <option key={cat} value={cat}>{cat}</option>)}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">SLA Priority</label>\n            <select value={priorityFilter} onChange={(e) => setPriorityFilter(e.target.value)} className=\"w-full h-8 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0c0c0c] px-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\">\n              <option value=\"all\">ALL PRIORITIES</option>\n              {PRIORITIES.map(prio => <option key={prio} value={prio}>{prio.toUpperCase()}</option>)}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">Linked Project</label>\n            <select value={projectFilter} onChange={(e) => setProjectFilter(e.target.value)} className=\"w-full h-8 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0c0c0c] px-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\">\n              <option value=\"all\">ALL PROJECTS</option>\n              {PROJECTS.map(proj => <option key={proj} value={proj}>{proj}</option>)}\n            </select>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/35 font-bold\">Operational Status</label>\n            <select value={statusFilter} onChange={(e) => setStatusFilter(e.target.value)} className=\"w-full h-8 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#0c0c0c] px-2 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\">\n              <option value=\"all\">ALL STATUSES</option>\n              <option value=\"open\">UNRESOLVED</option>\n              <option value=\"in_progress\">EVALUATING</option>\n              <option value=\"resolved\">SEALED (RESOLVED)</option>\n            </select>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 4. MAIN LAYOUT CONTAINER */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-12 gap-6 items-start\">\n        \n        {/* Create Form (Left column) */}\n        <div className=\"xl:col-span-4 space-y-4\">\n          <WorkspaceCard className=\"p-4 border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm space-y-4 text-left\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-white/5 pb-2\">\n              <MessageSquare className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase tracking-wider\">Launch Secure Support Wire</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            <form onSubmit={handleCreateTicket} className=\"space-y-3.5\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold\">Subject Summary</label>\n                <input\n                  required\n                  type=\"text\"\n                  placeholder=\"Replication delay on node primary core\"\n                  value={newSubject}\n                  onChange={e => setNewSubject(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-3 text-white text-[11px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 transition-all\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold\">Category</label>\n                  <select\n                    value={newCategory}\n                    onChange={e => setNewCategory(e.target.value as EnrichedSupportTicket[\"category\"])}\n                    className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-2 text-white text-[10px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\"\n                  >\n                    {CATEGORIES.map(cat => (\n                      <option key={cat} value={cat} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">{cat}</option>\n                    ))}\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold\">SLA Priority</label>\n                  <select\n                    value={newPriority}\n                    onChange={e => setNewPriority(e.target.value as EnrichedSupportTicket[\"priority\"])}\n                    className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-2 text-white text-[10px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\"\n                  >\n                    {PRIORITIES.map(prio => (\n                      <option key={prio} value={prio} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">{prio.toUpperCase()}</option>\n                    ))}\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold\">Target Project</label>\n                <select\n                  value={newProject}\n                  onChange={e => setNewProject(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-2.5 text-white text-[10px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 cursor-pointer uppercase appearance-none\"\n                >\n                  {PROJECTS.map(proj => (\n                    <option key={proj} value={proj} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c]\">{proj}</option>\n                  ))}\n                </select>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <label className=\"text-[8px] font-mono uppercase text-white/40 font-bold\">Diagnostic Telemetry Payload</label>\n                <textarea\n                  required\n                  placeholder=\"Paste secure enclave log payloads or trace hashes here...\"\n                  value={newDesc}\n                  onChange={e => setNewDesc(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full h-24 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 p-3 text-white text-[11px] outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 resize-none transition-all\"\n                />\n              </div>\n\n              <button type=\"submit\" className=\"w-full h-9 rounded bg-white hover:bg-white/90 text-black font-mono font-bold text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer\">\n                Establish Secure Wire\n              </button>\n            </form>\n          </WorkspaceCard>\n\n          <div className=\"p-3.5 rounded-xl border border-yellow-500/10 bg-yellow-500/[0.02] text-[10px] font-mono text-yellow-500/70 leading-relaxed flex gap-2.5 text-left\">\n            <AlertTriangle className=\"w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-yellow-500/90 mt-0.5\" />\n            <div>\n              <span className=\"font-bold text-yellow-500 uppercase block mb-0.5\">Operator Check Required</span>\n              Action logs are permanently shared directly with sovereign compliance auditors.\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Tickets and Details (Right columns) */}\n        <div className=\"xl:col-span-8 space-y-4\">\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-4\">\n            \n            {/* Ticket list panel */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 space-y-2 max-h-[580px] overflow-y-auto pr-1\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between px-1 font-mono text-[9px]\">\n                <span className=\"text-white/35 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">Secure Sockets</span>\n                <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/25 px-1.5 py-0.2 rounded font-bold\">\n                  {filteredTickets.length} / {tickets.length} WIRES\n                </span>\n              </div>\n\n              {filteredTickets.length === 0 ? (\n                <EmptyState\n                  title=\"No Sockets Open\"\n                  description=\"No secure wires match your parameters.\"\n                  actionLabel=\"Clear Filters\"\n                  onAction={() => {\n                    setSearchQuery(\"\");\n                    setCategoryFilter(\"all\");\n                    setPriorityFilter(\"all\");\n                    setProjectFilter(\"all\");\n                    setStatusFilter(\"all\");\n                  }}\n                />\n              ) : (\n                <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                  {filteredTickets.map(ticket => {\n                    const isSelected = selectedTicket && selectedTicket.id === ticket.id;\n                    return (\n                      <div\n                        key={ticket.id}\n                        onClick={() => setSelectedTicketId(ticket.id)}\n                        className={`group relative p-3 rounded-lg border transition-all duration-150 cursor-pointer text-left ${\n                          isSelected \n                            ? \"bg-[#0b1424]/30 border-[#009DFF]/30 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(0,157,255,0.02)]\" \n                            : \"bg-[#050505]/40 border-white/5 hover:border-white/10\"\n                        }`}\n                      >\n                        {isSelected && <div className=\"absolute left-0 top-3 bottom-3 w-1 rounded-r bg-[#009DFF]\" />}\n                        <div className=\"space-y-1.5 font-mono\">\n                          <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[8px] text-white/35\">\n                            <span>{ticket.id}</span>\n                            <span>{new Date(ticket.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <h4 className=\"text-[11.5px] font-bold text-white line-clamp-1\">{ticket.title}</h4>\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                            <span className={`px-1.5 py-0.2 rounded text-[8px] font-bold uppercase border ${getPriorityColor(ticket.priority)}`}>\n                              {ticket.priority}\n                            </span>\n                            <span className=\"px-1.5 py-0.2 rounded text-[8px] text-white/50 bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 uppercase truncate max-w-[80px]\">\n                              {ticket.category}\n                            </span>\n                            <div className=\"ml-auto flex items-center gap-1 text-[8.5px] text-white/30 uppercase\">\n                              <span className={`w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full ${\n                                ticket.status === \"resolved\" ? \"bg-emerald-400\" :\n                                ticket.status === \"in_progress\" ? \"bg-blue-400\" : \"bg-amber-400 animate-pulse\"\n                              }`} />\n                              <span>{ticket.status === \"resolved\" ? \"Sealed\" : ticket.status === \"in_progress\" ? \"Evaluating\" : \"Open\"}</span>\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      </div>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Conversation detail panel */}\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-7\">\n              {selectedTicket ? (\n                <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col min-h-[440px]\">\n                  \n                  {/* Header */}\n                  <div className=\"p-3.5 border-b border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] flex items-center justify-between gap-4 font-mono\">\n                    <div className=\"space-y-0.5 text-left\">\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                        <span className=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">{selectedTicket.id}</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-white/20\">•</span>\n                        <span className=\"text-[8.5px] text-white/40 uppercase font-semibold\">{selectedTicket.category}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight line-clamp-1\">{selectedTicket.title}</h3>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <button \n                      onClick={() => {\n                        const updated = tickets.map(t => {\n                          if (t.id === selectedTicket.id) {\n                            const next = t.status === \"open\" ? \"in_progress\" : t.status === \"in_progress\" ? \"resolved\" : \"open\";\n                            return { ...t, status: next };\n                          }\n                          return t;\n                        });\n                        setTickets(updated);\n                      }}\n                      className=\"px-2 py-0.8 rounded border border-white/15 bg-white/[0.01] text-[8.5px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all flex items-center gap-1 cursor-pointer shrink-0\"\n                    >\n                      <RefreshCw className=\"w-2.5 h-2.5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                      <span>Status</span>\n                    </button>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Specs */}\n                  <div className=\"p-2.5 bg-[#020202]/50 border-b border-white/5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 font-mono text-[9px] text-left\">\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-semibold\">Priority Bounds:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold uppercase\">{selectedTicket.priority}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-semibold\">Target Enclave:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-white font-bold truncate block max-w-[100px]\" title={selectedTicket.linkedProject}>{selectedTicket.linkedProject}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <span className=\"text-white/30 block uppercase font-semibold\">Link State:</span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold block\">SOCKET SECURED</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Body Payload */}\n                  <div className=\"p-3.5 bg-black/40 border-b border-white/5 space-y-1 text-left font-mono text-xs\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/30 text-[8.5px] uppercase font-bold block\">Diagnostics Payload</span>\n                    <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded bg-[#020202] border border-white/5 text-white/85 select-text overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap max-h-[100px]\">\n                      {selectedTicket.desc}\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Messages Feed */}\n                  <div className=\"flex-grow p-4.5 space-y-3.5 max-h-[220px] overflow-y-auto bg-[#020202]/30 text-left\">\n                    <div className=\"text-center\">\n                      <span className=\"text-[8px] font-mono text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold\">— SECURE OPERATION WIRE FEED —</span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    {selectedTicket.replies.map((rep, idx) => {\n                      const isClient = rep.sender.includes(\"Alexander\") || rep.sender.includes(\"Client\");\n                      return (\n                        <div key={idx} className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                          <div className={`flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[8.5px] font-mono ${isClient ? \"justify-end text-[#009DFF]\" : \"justify-start text-[#00FFC2]\"}`}>\n                            <span className=\"font-bold uppercase\">{rep.sender}</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-white/20\">•</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[8px] text-white/40\">{new Date(rep.timestamp).toLocaleTimeString([], { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' })}</span>\n                          </div>\n                          <div className={`flex ${isClient ? \"justify-end\" : \"justify-start\"}`}>\n                            <div className={`max-w-[90%] rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-mono select-text ${\n                              isClient ? \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 text-white\" : \"bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/15 text-white/95\"\n                            }`}>\n                              {rep.text}\n                            </div>\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                      );\n                    })}\n\n                    {syncing && (\n                      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono text-white/45\">\n                        <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 animate-spin text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n                        <span>Core systems engineer syncing...</span>\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n\n                  {/* Message Input Box */}\n                  <form onSubmit={handleSendReply} className=\"p-2.5 border-t border-white/5 bg-black/[0.2] flex gap-2\">\n                    <input\n                      type=\"text\"\n                      placeholder={selectedTicket.status === \"resolved\" ? \"Wire socket is sealed. Toggle Status button to reopen.\" : \"Transmit secured operational log reply...\"}\n                      disabled={selectedTicket.status === \"resolved\"}\n                      value={replyText}\n                      onChange={e => setReplyText(e.target.value)}\n                      className=\"flex-grow h-8.5 rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-black/40 px-3 text-xs text-white outline-none font-mono focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 disabled:opacity-40\"\n                    />\n                    <button\n                      type=\"submit\"\n                      disabled={!replyText.trim() || selectedTicket.status === \"resolved\"}\n                      className=\"h-8.5 w-8.5 rounded-lg bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] disabled:bg-white/5 disabled:text-white/20 text-white flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer shrink-0 transition-all shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(0,157,255,0.15)] disabled:shadow-none\"\n                    >\n                      <Send className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                    </button>\n                  </form>\n\n                </div>\n              ) : (\n                <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 text-center min-h-[360px] flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-2\">\n                  <HelpCircle className=\"w-10 h-10 text-white/15\" />\n                  <span className=\"text-white/35 font-mono text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest\">No Socket Selected</span>\n                  <p className=\"text-white/25 text-[10px] font-mono max-w-xs\">Select an active socket from the left list to review diagnostics and logs.</p>\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 5. EMERGENCY CTA BAR */}\n      <WorkspaceCard className=\"border border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#040914] to-[#010307] p-5 rounded-xl relative overflow-hidden text-left\">\n        <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-5 pointer-events-none\">\n          <ShieldCheck className=\"w-36 h-36 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-4 font-mono\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1.5 max-w-3xl\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[#009DFF]\">\n              <ShieldCheck className=\"w-4 h-4 animate-pulse\" />\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-bold tracking-widest uppercase\">Emergency Core Bypass Protocol</span>\n            </div>\n            <h4 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight\">Need immediate physical memory partition isolation?</h4>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed\">\n              If an active enclave breach is suspected, approved Level IV operators can trigger immediate virtual network decoupling and cryptographic rollover over high-priority hardware SLA.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <button \n            onClick={() => {\n              setSuccessToast(\"Emergency Decouple Broadcasted\");\n              setTimeout(() => setSuccessToast(null), 4000);\n            }}\n            className=\"inline-flex h-9 px-4 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white font-bold text-[9.5px] uppercase tracking-wider transition-all hover:shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(239,68,68,0.35)] active:scale-[0.98] cursor-pointer\"\n          >\n            Request Decoupling\n          </button>\n        </div>\n      </WorkspaceCard>\n\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
